tossup_question: -  Which of the following is NOT equal to a × log base b of c?
tossup_MCQoptions:
W) 1/a × log base b of the fraction a/c
X) –a × log base b of the fraction 1/c
Y) –log base b of open parenthesis c-a close parenthesis
Z) Natural log of (exp^a) × log base b of c
tossup_answer: ANSWER: W) 1/a × log BASE b OF THE FRACTION a/c
